{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 N2N Chooser\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is a helper plugin for the Numbers2Notes system. It allows you to tag tracks with specific "Roles" (e.g., Bass, Chords, Text Chart) so the main Numbers2Notes script knows where to generate content.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Visual Dashboard to assign track roles.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Generation ON/OFF toggle to protect tracks from updates.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Preferred Key selector for "Capo-style" transposition logic.\sa180\par}
}

