{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 EFFECTS\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab MidiOnOff - Simple Effect to turn MIDI on and OFF via MIDI\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaCenterMIDIpitch - Recenters MIDI pitches around a user definable center pitch.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaPulse - A specialized version of RCJach's MIDI Note Beat Repeater effect.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Swing Track MIDI - Applies swing to even eights from 0 to 100% on individual MIDI tracks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Swing Project MIDI - Applies swing to even eights from 0 to 100% across all tracks with the SwingTrackMIDI effect.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Wait-A-Moment - Sets a short delay compensation for MIDI arpeggiators.\sa180\par}
